FrontEnd: 

Dependancies:
    npm create vite@latest frontend -- --template react
    cd frontend
    npm install
    install nvm-windows
    npm install -D tailwindcss@latest postcss@latest autoprefixer@latest
    nvm install node
    npm install react-router-dom
    npm install axios
    npm install jwt-decode
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Pre-Production Checks:
    CORS_ALLOW_ALL_ORIGINS = True  # for development only TODO: Tighten allowed origins allowed list

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
How to run:
    start django server
        cd .\backend\
        python manage.py runserver
    start vite backend
        cd .\frontend\
        npm run dev